        {
            "title": "內地超長期低息車貸傳月底結束  汽車股捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地傳媒報道，超長期低息車貸將收緊，於4 月30日結束，汽車股捱沽。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251201_FI_source-web_02015-i6-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251201_FI_source-web_02015-i6-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：理想汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">理想汽車(02015) 挫4.65%，報69.75元；蔚來汽車(09866)跌5.66%，報48.02元 ; 奇瑞汽車(09973)跌3.89%，報30.64元；比亞迪(01211)跌3.58%，報99.8元；吉利汽車(00175)跌3.47%，報22.84元；零跑汽車(09863)跌3.27%，報46.68元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2026年初內地車市掀起超長周期低息車貸促銷。《21世紀經濟報道》了解到，這一超長周期貸款業務正在被收緊，多家車企已明確將相關政策延續至2026年4月30日，後續是否續期暫無定論。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道引述股份制銀行汽車金融人士透露，在銀行暫停車貸7年期之時，融資租賃公司也傳出要求停貸。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">小米汽車的一位銷售人員給《21世紀經濟報道》展示了其內部通知:接銀行政策調整通知，6至7年期産品可能隨時停止受理，最多做到4月30日。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15914685-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e8%b6%85%e9%95%b7%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%81%af%e8%bb%8a%e8%b2%b8%e5%82%b3%e6%9c%88%e5%ba%95%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f-%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e8%82%a1%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240714_CH_China-Road_source-web_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 11:55:06",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股半日挫  深股失萬五關  創板跌逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日跌，深股失守15000，跌逾1%，創業板指數跌2.2%，兩市成交合計17298.68億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日報4069點，跌23點或0.58%，今早開跌8點或0.19%，報4081點，早段見4084點，跌9點或0.21%，為半日高位，即反覆向下，最低見4061，踌2點或0.78%，為上午低位，半日成交7516.88億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日報14837，挫205點或1.37%，今早開跌92點或0.61%，報14951點，最高見14998，跌45點或0.29%，跌幅其後擴大，最低報14813，跌230點或1.52%，為半日低位，半日成交9781.8億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日報4745點，跌40點或0.85%，今早開跌15點或0.31%，報4771點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數挫81點或2.2%，報3638點，今早開跌1.02%或38點，報3682點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15914656-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%8c%ab-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%b1%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94%e9%97%9c-%e5%89%b5%e6%9d%bf%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 11:44:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股曾跌276點  晶片股逆市飆  經緯天地插水逾65%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數暫最低見25639，跌276點或1.06%，跌幅隨即收窄，最高見25828，跌87點或0.33%，現跌89點或0.35%，報25825點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數跌1點或0.04%，報4863 ; 國指點或0.08%，報8725點。 </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交 1092.33億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股造好，中芯(00981)揚7.7%，報62.95元 ，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 華虹半導體(01347)飆12.41%，報105.5元，ASMPT(00522)飛升7.44%，報166元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">汽車股捱沽，理想汽車(02015)跌5.33%，報69.25元 ，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 吉利(00175)跌3.3%，報22.88元 ; 比亞迪(01211)跌3.58%，報99.8元。寧德時代(03750)轉跌，跌2.21%，報687元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中電信(00728)跌2.94%，報4.96元 。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">聯想(00992)升2.58%，報11.94元 ; 信義玻璃(00868)升2.18%，報9.83元。升幅藍籌股中居二、三位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">經緯天地(02940)洗倉式下挫，插65.25%，報1.88元，曾跌68.39%，入20大成交額。在上午10:40出現大手賣出，成交量為360萬，成交價為3元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15914562-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c276%e9%bb%9e-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e9%a3%86-%e7%b6%93%e7%b7%af%e5%a4%a9%e5%9c%b0%e6%8f%92%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be65",
